description: The components and hardware used are some of the best available. The car is powered by a LS1 engine,automatic 4L80E transmission,very well detailed and finished under carriage. The engine compartment is done very well and shows wonderfully. The suspension and brakes have all been upgraded to Coilovers and Willwood 4 wheel disc all around. The car has a Ford 9”rear, tubular A arms, and upgraded supporting hardware and a Nice sounding FloMaster exhaust. The interior is very well done and has upgraded Autometer gauges,Custom Finished seating,Custom dash and console With Kenwood DVD/NAV System with Premier Speakers,Tilt steering column with cruise control,And Vintage air A/C System The paint is finished in a great Jade Green with silver stripes color combination that looks Amazing!
title: 1968 Chevrolet Camaro
